@startuml Irrigation_DatabaseFlow
!theme plain
title Match Monitor - Irrigation Detection - Database Flow (All SPs)

!define DB_COLOR #E3F2FD
!define SP_COLOR #FFF9C4
!define TABLE_COLOR #C8E6C9

' Databases
database "CTS_DataCenter" DB_COLOR {
  rectangle "SystemParameter" as SysParam TABLE_COLOR
  rectangle "MatchMonitorRuleSetting" as RuleSetting TABLE_COLOR
  rectangle "MatchMonitorStagingIrrigationNonLive\n(Pool 2006)" as Staging TABLE_COLOR
  rectangle "CTSMatchMonitor" as Match TABLE_COLOR
  rectangle "CTSMatchMonitorDetail" as Detail TABLE_COLOR
}

' Stored Procedures
rectangle "**Stored Procedures**" SP_COLOR {
  rectangle "SP 1: RuleIrrigation_Get\n(Get staging matches)" as SP1 #FFEB3B
  rectangle "SP 2: RuleIrrigation_Process\n(Detect irrigation pattern)" as SP2 #FFEB3B
  rectangle "SP 3: RuleIrrigation_Complete\n(Save results)" as SP3 #FFEB3B
  rectangle "SP 4: RuleIrrigation_TransClean\n(Clean staging)" as SP4 #FFEB3B
}

' SP1: Get staging matches
SP1 -down-> SysParam : READ LastScannedSequenceID\n(ParameterID = 125)\nREAD BatchSize\n(ParameterID = 124)
SP1 -down-> RuleSetting : READ MinTimeStep\n(RuleGroupID = 4)
SP1 -down-> Staging : **SELECT** matches\nWHERE SequenceID > LastScannedSequenceID\nGROUP BY MatchID, ScoreDiff, BettypeID,\n         BetID, HDP, Betteam\nLIMIT 5000

note bottom of SP1
  **Input:**
  - @ip_LiveIndicator = 0 (NonLive only)
  
  **Output:**
  - MatchStagingList (grouped by match characteristics)
  - @op_MaxSequenceID
  
  **Logic:**
  1. Get LastScannedSequenceID and BatchSize
  2. Get MinTimeStep from rule settings
  3. Calculate MaxTransDate based on TimeStep
  4. Query staging table for matches
  5. Group by match characteristics
  6. Return distinct match groups + MaxSequenceID
  
  **Key**: NO filtering by customer or association
end note

' SP2: Process Rule
SP2 -down-> Staging : **SELECT** all tickets\nWHERE MatchID, ScoreDiff, BettypeID,\n      BetID, HDP, Betteam match\nAND SequenceID <= MaxSequenceID
SP2 -down-> RuleSetting : **READ** TimeStep, TotalStake, OddsSpread\n(RuleGroupID = 4, SportType)
SP2 -down-> SysParam : **READ** LastScannedSequenceID\n(ParameterID = 125)

note bottom of SP2
  **Input:**
  - @ip_LiveIndicator = 0
  - @ip_MaxSequenceID
  - @ip_SportType, @ip_MatchID, @ip_ScoreDiff
  - @ip_BettypeID, @ip_BetID, @ip_HDP, @ip_Betteam
  
  **Logic:**
  1. Get all tickets for this match characteristic
  2. Get rule settings (TimeStep=180s, TotalStake=$1000, OddsSpread=28%)
  3. Calculate Old Groups (tickets <= LastScannedSequenceID)
     - GROUP BY CustID
     - Aggregate: MaxTransDate, TotalStake, Odds range
  4. Calculate New Groups (tickets > LastScannedSequenceID)
     - GROUP BY CustID
     - Aggregate: MinTransDate, TotalStake, Odds range
  5. Merge if TimeGap <= TimeStep
  6. For each customer:
     a. Check Total Stake >= $1000
     b. Calculate Odds Spread (same sign vs mixed sign)
     c. Check Odds Spread >= 28%
  7. Mark detected customers with GroupID = 1
  
  **Output:**
  - List of detected customers with irrigation pattern
  
  **KEY: NO Association Detection!**
  - Only analyze INDIVIDUAL customers
  - No Device/AI/IP queries
  - No cross-customer grouping
end note

' SP3: Complete
SP3 -down-> Match : **INSERT** detected matches\n(Reason = 'IR')
SP3 -down-> Detail : **INSERT** ticket details

note bottom of SP3
  **Input:**
  - @ip_LiveIndicator = 0
  - @ip_TransGroupJson (detected customers)
  - @ip_MaxSequenceID
  - Match info (MatchID, ScoreDiff, BettypeID, etc.)
  
  **Logic:**
  1. Parse TransGroupJson
     Format: [
       {
         "CustID": 12345,
         "GroupID": 1,
         "TotalStake": 1500,
         "TransIDList": "...",
         ...
       }
     ]
  2. INSERT into CTSMatchMonitor:
     - MatchID, ScoreDiff, BettypeID, BetID, HDP, Betteam
     - GroupID (unique per customer)
     - Reason = 'IR' (Irrigation)
     - TransIDList, CustIDList
     - TotalStake, OddsSpread
  3. INSERT into CTSMatchMonitorDetail:
     - All tickets for each customer
     - Link to CTSMatchMonitor via MatchID+GroupID
  
  **Tables Updated:**
  - CTSMatchMonitor (match level, per customer)
  - CTSMatchMonitorDetail (ticket level)
end note

' SP4: Clean
SP4 -down-> Staging : **DELETE** processed tickets\nWHERE SequenceID <= MaxSequenceID

note bottom of SP4
  **Input:**
  - @ip_LiveIndicator = 0
  - @ip_MaxSequenceID
  
  **Logic:**
  1. DELETE from MatchMonitorStagingIrrigationNonLive
  2. WHERE SequenceID <= MaxSequenceID
  3. Free space for next batch
  
  **Purpose:**
  - Clean processed tickets
  - Prevent duplicate processing
  - Maintain staging table size
end note

' Flow annotations
note as N1
  **Complete Flow Sequence:**
  
  1. SP1: Get Staging Matches
     └─ Read: SystemParameter, RuleSetting, Staging
     └─ Output: MatchStagingList + MaxSequenceID
  
  2. SP2: Process Rule (NO Association!)
     ├─ Read: Staging tickets per match
     ├─ Group by Customer (CustID)
     ├─ Calculate Old + New groups
     ├─ Merge if within TimeStep
     ├─ Validate: TotalStake >= $1000
     ├─ Calculate Odds Spread (2 formulas)
     ├─ Validate: OddsSpread >= 28%
     └─ Output: Detected customers
  
  3. SP3: Complete (Save Results)
     ├─ Parse TransGroupJson
     ├─ INSERT: CTSMatchMonitor (Reason='IR')
     └─ INSERT: CTSMatchMonitorDetail
  
  4. SP4: Clean Staging
     └─ DELETE processed tickets from staging
end note

' Table details
note right of Staging
  **MatchMonitorStagingIrrigationNonLive**
  (Pool 2006)
  
  Source: Insert Ticket Detail job
  Frequency: Every 5 minutes
  
  Key Fields:
  - SequenceID (incremental)
  - MatchID, ScoreDiff, BettypeID, BetID, HDP, Betteam
  - CustID, Stake, Odds
  - TransDate, TransID
  - SignNumber (sign of odds: +1 or -1)
end note

note right of Match
  **CTSMatchMonitor**
  
  Stores detected irrigation patterns
  
  Key Fields:
  - MatchID, GroupID (PK)
    (GroupID = per customer)
  - Reason = 'IR' (Irrigation)
  - ScoreDiff, BettypeID, BetID, HDP, Betteam
  - CustID (single customer!)
  - TransIDList (comma-separated)
  - TotalStake, OddsSpread
  - InsertTime
end note

note right of Detail
  **CTSMatchMonitorDetail**
  
  Stores individual tickets
  
  Key Fields:
  - MatchID, GroupID, TransID (PK)
  - CustID (same customer as CTSMatchMonitor)
  - Stake, Odds
  - TransDate
  - Reason = 'IR'
end note

note right of RuleSetting
  **MatchMonitorRuleSetting**
  (RuleGroupID = 4)
  
  Default Settings:
  - TimeStep: 180 seconds (3 min)
  - TotalStake: $1000
  - OddsSpread: 28%
  - SportType: Soccer (1)
  - Reason: 58 (Irrigation)
end note

note as N2
  **KEY DIFFERENCE:**
  
  Unlike other rules (GB, Saba GB, Hedging, Arbitrage, Parlay),
  Irrigation does NOT query association tables:
  
  ❌ NO CTS_DC_Association_Device_Get
  ❌ NO CTS_DC_Association_AI_Get
  ❌ NO CTS_DC_Association_IP_Get
  
  ✅ Only queries staging table
  ✅ Only groups by CustID
  ✅ Simplest database flow
end note

@enduml

